OL,3,CCCTV captures thieves breaking into
OL,4,Chome leaving couple 'afraid and
OL,5,Cvulnerable'
OL,7,FEmma Wilkinson reports
OL,9,FA couple felt afraid and vulnerable in
OL,10,Ftheir own home after two men ransacked
OL,11,Ftheir house and stole precious
OL,12,Fjewellery worth tens of thousands of
OL,13,Fpounds.
OL,15,FThe thieves were caught on CCTV
OL,16,Fbreaking into Charon and Kevin Mills'
OL,17,Fhome in Auckley late on the 18 August.
