OL,7,FShortly after 11pm, camera footage
OL,8,Fcaptured two hooded men, with a ladder
OL,9,Fin tow, arriving at the home they've
OL,10,Flived in for nearly 40 years.
OL,12,FThey had ripped out the alarm system
OL,13,Fand smashed through the door.
OL,15,FThey didn't leave a drawer unopened in
OL,16,Ftheir search for things to steal,
OL,17,Fleaving with a collection of family
OL,18,Fjewellery, including Charon's mum's
OL,19,Fwedding ring.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/9
