OL,7,FHer mum had lived with them four years
OL,8,Fago until her death.
OL,10,FCharon said, "Some of the things she
OL,11,Fleft, they had been in that and that's
OL,12,Fwhat I can't cope with. I just thank
OL,13,FGod that nobody was hurt.
OL,15,F"I get insecure, these people know who
OL,16,Fyou are, but you don't know who they
OL,17,Fare and it's not a nice feeling.
