OL,7,FAfter leaving the house, the
OL,8,Fperpetrators returned just an hour
OL,9,Flater - at around 1:15am - to take two
OL,10,Fvehicles. One of the vehicles, a work
OL,11,Fvan, was later found abandoned and
OL,12,Frecovered by police.
OL,14,FThe couple were on holiday at the time
OL,15,Fand are grateful to Charon's brother
OL,16,Ffor clearing up before they arrived
OL,17,Fhome, sparing them having to see the
OL,18,Ffull state of the house.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/9
