OL,7,FKevin said, "We've worked hard for
OL,8,Fwhat we've got, and these people think
OL,9,Fthey've got the sole right to break
OL,10,Finto people's homes and take what
OL,11,Fisn't theirs.
OL,13,F"Charon won't even look at the photos,
OL,14,Fif she saw them then I think she'd
OL,15,Fwant to move straight away. She
OL,16,Fcouldn't bear to see her home like it
OL,17,Fwas. It's heartbreaking for me to see
OL,18,Fher like she is.
OL,20,FKevin is now appealing for anyone with
OL,21,Finformation to help trace the suspects.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/9
