OL,7,F"The way they walked off is like they
OL,8,Fwalked out of the pub, not a care in
OL,9,Fthe world, and they'll continue doing
OL,10,Fit until people get caught. They need
OL,11,Fto get these lot."
OL,13,FLatest figures from the Office for
OL,14,FNational Statistics show from the year
OL,15,Fto March 2024 the residential burglary
OL,16,Frate in England was 7.5 per 1000
OL,17,Fhouseholds.
