OL,7,FIn Yorkshire and the Humber the rate
OL,8,Fwas 10.6, but in South Yorkshire, it's
OL,9,Falmost double the England average, at
OL,10,F14.3 per 1000.
OL,12,FIn a statement South Yorkshire Police
OL,13,Fsaid a special burglary team is
OL,14,Fworking to identify those responsible
OL,15,Ffor breaking into the Mills' home, and
OL,16,Fcontinues to work through a number of
OL,17,Flines of enquiry.
OL,19,FThe force added:
