OL,7,F"In Doncaster, Operation Castle was
OL,8,Flaunched to provide a dedicated and
OL,9,Fdetective-led response to incidents of
OL,10,Fburglary in people's homes in the
OL,11,Fcity. It has resulted in Doncaster
OL,12,Frecording its lowest number of
OL,13,Fburglaries in the past five years."
